shearers' whare
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a short-term lodging-house on a farm or station.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
